Package org.ginsim.core.graph.objectassociation

Interface GraphAssociatedObjectManager<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - manager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvatarParametersManager, BasicGraphAssociatedManager, BiblioManager, NamedStatesManager, PerturbationManager, ReductionConfigManager, SimulationParametersManager, StatesToHierarchicalMappingManager
    public interface GraphAssociatedObjectManager<T>
    Implement this interface to save/open objects associated to graph automatically.
    Author:
    Lionel Spinelli
